text: ve aise log hai jinhen hamane kitaab aur nirnay-shakti aur paigambaree pradaan kee thee (usee prakaar hamane muhammad ko bhee kitaab, nirnay-shakti aur paigambaree dee hai) . phir yadi ye log ise maarane se inakaar karen, to ab hamane isako aise logon ko saumpa hai jo isaka inakaar nahin karate
